#- PsychoPanda32 is borrowing 1d from the Nine Fund to purchase J3, J4, I3, I4.

The fund will provide 1d as a loan.

This is a binding agreement under the Nine Fund Loan Terms 2013-1.
#- One repayment of 1.5d is due on the 30th of March, 10:00pm Eastern time (GMT-5).

The overdue payment fee will be 0.5d. The loan will be secured against the plots purchased.
#- 